                    ],
                    Texts: [
                        {
                            Text: "Fourth tree — careful. That Field Agent has stood under it all week. He is forbidden from starting anything. Starting things is apparently a head office privilege. He steps between you and the seal anyway, smiling like a form letter."
                        }
                    ],
                    Name: "The fourth seal — the Field Agent",
                    Label: "seal_four"
                },
                {
                    Priority: -1,
