                    Texts: [
                        {
                            Text: "A field memo, folded twice, stamped for internal distribution. Determination 7-12, commodity pilot review. Honey — REJECTED. Supply diffuse, producers uncooperative, assets mobile and armed. Wheat — APPROVED. Centralized intake, predictable yield, granary infrastructure in place. Proceed to Hua Zhan."
                        }
                    ],
                    Name: "The field memo",
                    Label: "field_memo"
